description:
Fatal Fixation



Aired on 03/11/2013, Narrated by: Jonathan Aris



On 28 December 1978, the crew of United Airlines Flight 173, a Douglas DC-8-61, is preoccupied with a flikering landing gear light problem as the aircraft circles in a holding pattern in the vicinity of Portland, Oregon. It runs out of fuel and crashes in a sparsely populated area, killing 10 and seriously injuring 24 of the 189 on board.
